></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Boanerges</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">There have been 2 major reasons behind the increase in Dawnfires...<P>The first is the proliferation of epics. Why use a Dawnfire over an epic? Yes, I like to melee a bit but it's rare to find areas to hunt that are filled with undead. PLUS you have to be in a group to use it. Even with 1k AC most exp giving undead mobs would own me long before I could get enough procs to kill a mob. On top of all of this is you need a low risk scenario to melee period.<P>The second reason is the revamp of Fear has given us more potential drops of Dawnfires more frequently. Pre-revamp, Dawnfires were rare as crap (maybe 1 CT in 20 would drop one).<P>My 2cp? If you don't have your epic or some equivalent (ie Sacrifice) then Dawnfire is THE best option for your weapon hand.<P>------------------<BR>Boanerges Thundercry<BR>Erudite Templar of Prexus<BR><A HREF="http://www.cohort.cc" TARGET=_blank>Cohort Chalybeius</A><BR>Cazic Thule Server</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Scoral</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Cory add a third please)got mine fri...was a hard as hell camp and dread dropped it...i was amazed as i have been on many many fear raids (even after the buff) and never saw one drop...but i had hopes and they paid off)</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Corynthia</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">woohoo gratz Scoral  <IMG SRC="http://eqcleric.gameglow.com/ubb/smile.gif"><P>------------------<BR>Corynthia<BR>55th Level Dwarven Templar<BR>United Kingdom<BR>Bristlebane</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#f7f7f7"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Splaktar</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Before the upgrade I saw about 5 drop in 20 slayings of CT (once was duel wielding them).  After the upgrade I haven't spent all that much time in Fear, and usually only for CT himself.  So I've yet to see a Dawnfire drop there (only killed 5 golems or so since patch, dropped crappy shield and golem balls).  Tho I have seen a lot of clerics walking around with Dawnfires and Truesight Hammers lately.<P>------------------<BR>Splaktar/Gurgel/Samas</FONT></TD></TR><TR bgcolor="#dedfdf"><TD valign=top><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Arum EvilOne</FONT></TD><TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">With all the epics and stuff Dawnfire is ALOT easier to get ahold of. I picked up mine for 10k in EC. And if you just want some mace to swing around with, and feel a uber with, Dawnfire is hands down the best there is</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>
